<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TotoMagicien - Gagne avec style</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --gold: #FFD700;
            --gold-dark: #B8860B;
            --green-free: #00E676;
            --blue-tennis: #FF6B35;
            --purple-rare: #9C27B0;
            --telegram: #0088cc;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a0a2e 50%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ===== PARTICULES ===== */
        .particles {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 3px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 12s infinite;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
            10% { opacity: 0.5; }
            90% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) rotate(720deg); opacity: 0; }
        }

        /* ===== HEADER ===== */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: logoPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes logoPulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.3)); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.02); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(255,215,0,0.6)); }
        }

        .logo-container img {
            width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-top: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD700, #FFA500, #FFD700);
            background-size: 200% auto;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: shine 3s linear infinite;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        @keyframes shine {
            to { background-position: 200% center; }
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* ===== SECTION PACKS ===== */
        .packs-section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--gold);
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
        }

        .packs-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }

        /* ===== CARTE PACK ===== */
        .pack-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(26,26,26,0.95), rgba(10,10,10,0.98));
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .pack-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent 30%);
            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .pack-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.08;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .pack-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
            border-color: var(--gold);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
        }

        .pack-card.featured {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
            transform: scale(1.03);
            animation: featuredGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes featuredGlow {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,215,0,0.2); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(255,215,0,0.4), 0 0 120px rgba(255,215,0,0.1); }
        }

        .pack-card.featured:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.05);
        }

        .pack-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 12px;
            right: 12px;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            animation: badgePulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .badge-gratuit { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00C853, #00E676); color: #000; }
        .badge-tennis { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E); color: #fff; }
        .badge-populaire { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9C27B0, #E040FB); color: #fff; }
        .badge-best { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FFA500); color: #000; }

        @keyframes badgePulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* ===== IMAGE JOUEUR ===== */
        .player-img-container {
            width: 160px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s;
        }

        .pack-card:hover .player-img-container {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .player-img-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.4s;
        }

        .pack-card:hover .player-img-container img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .player-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.9), transparent);
        }

        .pack-name {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* ===== PRIX ANIMÉS ===== */
        .pack-price {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 12px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        }

        .pack-price .currency {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .pack-price .period {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }

        .price-counter {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: pricePop 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes pricePop {
            0% { transform: scale(0) rotate(-10deg); opacity: 0; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.2) rotate(5deg); }
            100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .pack-features {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .pack-features li {
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .pack-features li::before {
            content: '✦';
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* ===== TIMER ===== */
        .timer-box {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 8px;
            margin: 12px 0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: none;
        }

        .timer-box.active {
            display: block;
            animation: timerSlide 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes timerSlide {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .timer-box span {
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* ===== BOUTON MAGIQUE AVEC EFFET CLIC ===== */
        .magic-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--black);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #FFA500);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            user-select: none;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        .magic-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
        }

        .magic-btn:active::before {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }

        .magic-btn::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .magic-btn:hover::after {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .magic-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255,215,0,0.4);
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .magic-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(-1px) scale(0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
        }

        /* Effet ripple au clic */
        .ripple {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            transform: scale(0);
            animation: rippleEffect 0.6s linear;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        @keyframes rippleEffect {
            to {
                transform: scale(4);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        .magic-btn.free {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00C853, #00E676);
            color: white;
        }

        .magic-btn.free:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,200,83,0.4);
        }

        .magic-btn.tennis {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
        }

        .magic-btn.rare {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9C27B0, #E040FB);
            color: white;
        }

        .magic-btn.alpha {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FF8C00);
            color: #000;
        }

        /* ===== SECTION FIABILITÉ (STATS SEULEMENT) ===== */
        .fiabilite-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(255,215,0,0.03), transparent);
        }

        .fiabilite-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .fiabilite-container h2 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(26,26,26,0.9), rgba(10,10,10,0.95));
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .stat-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,215,0,0.05), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .stat-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255,215,0,0.1);
        }

        .stat-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }

        .stat-number-big {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--gold);
            display: block;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
            animation: countUp 2s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes countUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .stat-label-big {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* ===== SECTION TELEGRAM ===== */
        .telegram-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .telegram-card {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(0,136,204,0.08), rgba(0,0,0,0.9));
            border: 2px solid rgba(0,136,204,0.3);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .telegram-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, transparent, #0088cc, transparent 30%);
            animation: rotate 8s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.03;
        }

        .telegram-card:hover {
            border-color: #0088cc;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,136,204,0.2);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .telegram-icon-big {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: telegramBounce 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        @keyframes telegramBounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(3deg); }
        }

        .telegram-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: white;
        }

        .telegram-card p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .telegram-stats-inline {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tg-stat {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tg-stat-number {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #0088cc;
            display: block;
        }

        .tg-stat-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .telegram-btn-big {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0088cc, #00a8e8);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .telegram-btn-big::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .telegram-btn-big:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .telegram-btn-big:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,136,204,0.5);
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .telegram-btn-big:active {
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(0.98);
        }

        /* ===== EBOOK ===== */
        .ebook-section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(107,33,168,0.05), transparent);
        }

        .ebook-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .ebook-images {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .ebook-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            transition: transform 0.4s;
        }

        .ebook-img:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(1deg);
        }

        .ebook-content h2 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .ebook-content p {
            color: #bbb;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* ===== CGU ===== */
        .cgu-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.96);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .cgu-modal {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1a1a, #0a0a0a);
            border: 2px solid var(--gold);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 35px;
            max-width: 650px;
            max-height: 85vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .cgu-modal h2 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .cgu-modal p {
            color: #bbb;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .cgu-modal button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #FFA500);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .cgu-modal button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,215,0,0.3);
        }

        /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
            .packs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .pack-card.featured { transform: scale(1); }
            .pack-card.featured:hover { transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02); }
            .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .stat-number-big { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .ebook-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .telegram-stats-inline { gap: 20px; }
            .telegram-card { padding: 35px 20px; }
            .telegram-btn-big { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        }

        /* ===== ANIMATIONS ENTRÉE ===== */
        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .delay-5 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- PARTICULES -->
    <div class="particles" id="particles"></div>

    <!-- CGU MODAL -->
    <div class="cgu-overlay" id="cguModal">
        <div class="cgu-modal">
            <h2>🔥 Conditions Générales</h2>
            <p><strong>Article 1 :</strong> Pronostics à titre indicatif, résultats non garantis.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 2 :</strong> Tu dois être majeur. Joue responsablement.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 3 :</strong> Contenu propriété exclusive TotoMagicien™.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 4 :</strong> Nous déclinons toute responsabilité en cas de pertes.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 5 :</strong> Les prix sont susceptibles de changer sans préavis.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 6 :</strong> En acceptant, tu consens à rejoindre notre communauté Telegram.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 7 :</strong> Le pack gratuit est limité à 1 essai par personne.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 8 :</strong> Tout litige relève du droit français.</p>
            <button onclick="acceptCGU()">✨ J'ACCEPTE ✨</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="images/logo.png" alt="TotoMagicien">
        </div>
        <h1>TotoMagicien</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Gagne avec style • Pronostics VIP • Analyses Pro</p>
    </header>

